pullsbody:
Clean up build system a bit to use pkg-config instead of hard-coded libs

Builds on Fedora 15 x64 and Ubuntu 11.04 x32

Incorporates some of derf's changes, and fixes destination-overflow bugs in several strncpy/strcpy's.

Also cleaned up some but not all minor new things flagged by gcc 4.5 (I added some compiler options that suppress the errors for these things, which were new in 4.5)
pull_repo_desc: Ikran, an addon for Mozilla for making audio/video call using SIP
pull_commit_message: Initial checkin of x64 changes and build cleanup
